Parameters

Name
Type: SystemString
The name of an existing spandrel
NumberStories
Type: SystemInt32
The number of stories that the spandrel exists on and for which section properties are provided
StoryName
Type: SystemString
This is an array that includes the story names at which the spandrel exists
NumAreaObj
Type: SystemInt32
This is an array that includes the number of area objects in the spandrel at each story
NumLineObj
Type: SystemInt32
This is an array that includes the number of line objects in the spandrel at each story
Length
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the spandrel length
DepthLeft
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the spandrel depth at the left end
ThickLeft
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the spandrel thickness at the left end
DepthRight
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the spandrel depth at the right end
ThickRight
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the spandrel thickness at the right end
MatProp
Type: SystemString
This is an array that includes the pier material property
CGLeftX
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the x-coordinate of the center of gravity at the left end of the spandrel
CGLeftY
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the y-coordinate of the center of gravity at the left end of the spandrel
CGLeftZ
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the z-coordinate of the center of gravity at the left end of the spandrel
CGRightX
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the x-coordinate of the center of gravity at the right end of the spandrel
CGRightY
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the y-coordinate of the center of gravity at the right end of the spandrel
CGRightZ
Type: SystemDouble
This is an array that includes the z-coordinate of the center of gravity at the right end of the spandrel

Return Value

Type: Int32
Returns zero if the data is successfully retrieved; otherwise it returns a nonzero value
